2. **🚨 MANDATORY: ALWAYS read `../compliance/.cursorrules-compliance-checklist` BEFORE ANY RESPONSE** - **NO EXCEPTIONS**
3. **🚨 MANDATORY: ALWAYS read `../system/.cursorrules-dependency-mapper` FOR DEPENDENCY CHAIN** - **NO EXCEPTIONS**
4. **🚨 MANDATORY: ALWAYS read `../compliance/.cursorrules-compliance-monitor` FOR REAL-TIME MONITORING** - **NO EXCEPTIONS**
5. **🚨 MANDATORY: ALWAYS read `../system/.cursorrules-emergency-protocol` FOR VIOLATION HANDLING** - **NO EXCEPTIONS**
6. **🚨 MANDATORY: ALWAYS read `../system/.cursorrules-system-override` FOR SYSTEM ENFORCEMENT** - **NO EXCEPTIONS**

**⚠️ CRITICAL: ALWAYS read this rule file first before executing any AEM template creation tasks:**
1. **🚨 MANDATORY: ALWAYS read the rule file first** - **NO EXCEPTIONS**
